ZH: 不要因为心情不好而冲昏头脑做出决定。
EN: Don't make decisions when your mind is clouded by emotions.

ZH: 他在喝醉了酒之后就容易冲昏头脑。
EN: He tends to have clouded judgment after drinking.

ZH: 我们不能让恐惧和焦虑冲昏头脑。
EN: We cannot let fear and anxiety cloud our judgment.

